{"TopicId":194449,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Easier \u201Cswitch to\u201D for rendezvous?","CreatedByName":"jcharney","CreatedById":205128,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-04T19:44:15Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"jcharney","CreatedById":205128,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-04T19:44:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there an easier way to switch to a closeby target in map mode without going to the tracking station? If two crafts are\u00A0anywhere close to each other, it\u2019s hard to get the mouse to highlight the correct target to click in Map Mode and\u00A0\u201Cswitch to\u201D controlling them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-04T19:48:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you\u0027re within physics range, which IIRC is 2.2km, then you can switch using [ and ].\u00A0 In flight, you can just press M to go to map mode and switch there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-06-04T19:51:25Z\u0022 title=\u002206/04/2020 07:51  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EJune 4, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Geonovast\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EMis-read question\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-04T20:28:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you don\u0027t mind mods try Targets in for those vessels nearby but not nearby enough.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002289502\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed6185784692\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/105730-18x-targetron-continued-bis-wathever-163-20191023/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:213px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jcharney","CreatedById":205128,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-05T20:21:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you so much, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/179753-geonovast/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022179753\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/179753-geonovast/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Geonovast\u003C/a\u003E! The [ ] is exactly what I needed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Curveball Anders","CreatedById":107529,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-06T14:51:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223797174\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022194449\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221591300128\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 6/4/2020 at 9:48 PM, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you\u0027re within physics range, which IIRC is 2.2km, then you can switch using [ and ].\u00A0 In flight, you can just press M to go to map mode and switch there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr whatever on your keyboard, but might be adjusted in settings.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}